Package: freedom
Title: Demonstration of Disease Freedom (DDF)
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Rosendal", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "trosendal@gmail.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6576-9668"))
Description: Yet another R-package that implements the formulae
    required to calculate freedom from disease according to Cameron
    and Baldock (1998). These are the methods used at the Swedish
    national veterinary institute (SVA) to evaluate the performatnce
    of our nation animal disease surveillance programmes.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/SVA-SE/freedom
BugReports: https://github.com/SVA-SE/freedom/issues
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
